<HEADLINE> World Bank Vows East Timor Support </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WASHINGTON (AP) -- The World Bank is ready to offer financial  
support to a new government in East Timor as the province moves 
toward independence from Indonesia, Bank President James Wolfensohn 
said Tuesday. 
